title: BONUS: Katie Cazorla Talks 'Second Wives Club' and RHONY
description:
Katie Cazorla of "Second Wives Club" is, like, famous now; so naturally we had to hear how her life has changed. Come join us as we talk shit about each other, Second Wives Club, and Real Housewives of New York!
